{"tid":1268624,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［相由心生係真］見識過今日藍屍集會，無一個人係正常樣","createTime":"2019-06-30T10:36:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T03:40:25.000Z","uid":70888,"like":47,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"03959b5843c806f9a9cf0a75e056669967991aa6","tid":1268624,"uid":70888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T10:36:11.000Z","msg":"廢老，弱智，八婆，賤種，畸胎 樣樣齊<br />\n相由心生原來係真既。<br />\n<br />\n真正香港人憑樣就識別到，聽日71 真香港人要將藍屍踐踏個既地方重新整頓好<br />\n<br />\n以後我唔撚會禮讓一睇就知藍絲樣既人，社會垃圾，屌你老母<br />\n<br />\n同埋如果聽日有藍絲挑釁，咪撚阻住身邊人打鳩佢地，今日佢地打鳩完人 無事返屋企，依家一肚火屌佢地老母"},{"pid":"7cb4f1c8d4893deae369b3d6ecaf4c3108f13137","tid":1268624,"uid":267801,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T10:39:23.000Z","msg":"一如既往遍地垃圾。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aaLVUHG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaaLVUHG.jpg&h=2b4413ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UGFyGnJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUGFyGnJ.jpg&h=3c436077&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z34GQf4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz34GQf4.jpg&h=4721152f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b09cd5890d2fa6af2cd922b077bc780743e56089","tid":1268624,"uid":70888,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T10:39:47.000Z","msg":"聽日比藍絲挑釁既話，唔該和理非行開，唔好叫咩 唔好打<br />\n<br />\n依家我地既同伴比藍絲打撚到仆街 都無事，佢地仲要拍撚晒片都唔撚驚<br />\n<br />\n點都要報仇，屌佢地老母"},{"pid":"fa8598f9979d95a2cf8b236c1b31c4104c6d143f","tid":1268624,"uid":70888,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T10:40:30.000Z","msg":"勇武做野，唔該和理非咪撚阻止<br />\n各有各做"},{"pid":"0b23b297806a56b7acac7e2d90f7a1103ca016e5","tid":1268624,"uid":5523,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T10:40:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0ed655bae9b4b968b42e654da95ce54237b8e3a","tid":1268624,"uid":70888,"